### ‚ö° Quick Discovery Flow (6 Steps)

Each step must include **specific, copy-paste-ready language**.

1. **Opening Authority Position**  
   ‚Äú[Contact Name], I‚Äôve worked with [type of companies] on [specific challenge]. [Brief insight]. Does that resonate with your situation?‚Äù
