   ‚Äú[Specific follow-up that quantifies or expands the consequence]‚Äù
1. **Future State Vision**  
   ‚ÄúIf you could solve [specific pain], what would that mean for [their goal]?‚Äù
1. **Impact Quantification**  
   ‚ÄúWhen [specific pain] persists, what‚Äôs the cost in [time/money/opportunity]?‚Äù
1. **Next Steps**  
   ‚ÄúBased on what you‚Äôve shared, [specific next step] makes sense. Does [timeframe] work?‚Äù

